e poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/de083234324a02844c502283ab73c39a.poster.avif?t=1707145365\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/de083234324a02844c502283ab73c39a.webm?t=1707145365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/de083234324a02844c502283ab73c39a.mp4?t=1707145365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Engaging linear story: </strong>Unravel the story of the UFO's escape as you progress through the levels, adding an extra layer of depth and engagement to the gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/431cb2619fbf3559a0e7b72a44e46f8c.poster.avif?t=1707145365\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/431cb2619fbf3559a0e7b72a44e46f8c.webm?t=1707145365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/431cb2619fbf3559a0e7b72a44e46f8c.mp4?t=1707145365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Retro-gamer appeal:</strong> With its challenging puzzles and arcade-style gameplay, Korlax Escape is sure to resonate with fans of classic games and those who enjoy the retro gaming aesthetic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/2f1209aa2621bb19ca988492dfc2fc2d.poster.avif?t=1707145365\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229470/extras/2f1209aa2621bb19ca988492dfc2fc2d.webm?t=1707145365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9